title: Welcome to Kiron Ang’s Personal Website!
text: My name is Kiron Ang, and I’m an undergraduate student at Baylor University! I currently live in Waco, TX as I pursue a Bachelor of Science in Informatics. I plan to graduate in December 2025 unless something goes horribly wrong.

title: Blog
text:
Here, I will take note of some interesting things that have happened in my life recently so you can get to know me better!
Always make sure to check back for new updates; I will NOT store old posts anywhere.
